Package: python3-tm-librarian
Architecture: all
Depends: python3 (>= 3.2),
	${python3:Depends},
	${misc:Depends}
Description: Python3 files for The Machine from HPE
 Executable and library code for tm-librarian and tm-lfs, both per-node and
 Top of Rack Management Server (ToRMS)

Package: tm-librarian
Architecture: all
Depends: python3 (>= 3.2),
	python3-tm-librarian,
	python3-flask,
	${misc:Depends}
Recommends: attr
Description: Librarian for The Machine from HPE
 Database constructor, checker, and central daemon for the Librarian
 File System (LFS) suite for The Machine from Hewlett Packard Enterprise.
 The LFS Management Protocol (LMP) is also configured with this package.

Package: tm-lfs
Architecture: all
Depends: python3 (>= 3.2),
	python3-tm-librarian,
	tm-libfuse,
	${misc:Depends}
Description: Librarian File System daemon for The Machine from HPE
 Librarian File System daemon for each node in The Machine.  It needs
 to connect with a Librarian cental daemon.
